name: RV
text:
Kids love being here.. Nice people 👍

They have goats rabbits horses ducks roosters and playground swings.. lots of fun for kids

resp.text: Thank you so much! We really enjoyed you and your family being here for the birthday party, come back and see us!

name: JoHanna Ellerbe
text: We went on a class field trip and my daughter loved it. Very educational

resp.text: Thank you so much for your review! We are so glad that y’all enjoyed your time, please come back and see us soon!

name: Charybdis ¿?
text: My son went on a class field trip! Such a cute place! It's small but very very fun! My son had a blast and made lots of lasting memories!

resp.text: We are so glad he had a great time! Our pledge to y’all is to make this your best field trip ever, we are so glad he made lots of memories!

name: Mary Jane McGugin
text: We had our son's birthday here, super nice people and the place is so nice. Fun pony rides and a bunch of animals...plus a playground for the kids. Would have another party here. Thanks

resp.text: Thank you so much for your review! We are so glad you enjoyed our place and the animals. Please come back and see us soon!

name: Joe Fail
text: Had a 5 year old birthday party and was very pleased with the area and the animals are great for children who love animals!

resp.text: Thank you so much for the kind review. We really appreciated your business!

name: Charles Harvey
text:
Great place for younger studdnts to learn
using hands on and visual aids.
Great for over night events and birthday parties.

resp.text: Thank you for your review! We really appreciate it!!

name: Deb G
text: Really great place for kids entertaining and fun farm experience

resp.text: We are so glad you enjoyed your time here! Please come back and see us again!
